00:04:24.185 --> 00:04:27.090
Wasn't really, doesn't really matter what the shape of the lens was,

78
00:04:27.090 --> 00:04:30.665
we're only retaining the quadratic terms so, unsurprisingly,

79
00:04:30.665 --> 00:04:35.140
we find a quadratic form for the optical path length.

80
00:04:35.140 --> 00:04:37.860
The interesting bit is what's in parentheses here,

81
00:04:37.860 --> 00:04:39.205
because this is an old friend.

