00:05:06.685 --> 00:05:09.400
so I can put any constant I want in here.

91
00:05:09.400 --> 00:05:11.835
Constant optical path lengths aren't interesting,

92
00:05:11.835 --> 00:05:13.510
it's only their shape that matters.

